-- Germany says role in D.Boerse, NYSE merger limited
-- 
-- Mon Feb 14, 2011 9:46am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/14/us-nyse-deutscheboerse-germany-idUSTRE71D23W20110214

 

 BERLIN  (Reuters) - The German government has only a limited role in the merger planned between Deutsche Boerse and NYSE Euronext, a finance ministry spokesman said on Monday. 

 "The role of the government with regards to the merger is limited. These are two private companies," finance ministry spokesman Martin Kreienbaum said. (Reporting by  Noah Barkin  and  Brian Rohan )